OL,3,CFarage pledges 'mass deportation' of
OL,4,Csmall boat arrivals in Reform plans
OL,6,FNigel Farage is to publish plans for
OL,7,Fmass deportations of asylum seekers
OL,8,Fwho come to the UK on small boats
OL,9,Fwhich his Reform UK party would seek
OL,10,Fto put in place if it entered
OL,11,Fgovernment.
OL,13,FArresting asylum seekers on arrival,
OL,14,Fautomatic detention and forced
OL,15,Fdeportation to countries such as
OL,16,FAfghanistan and Eritrea are among the
OL,17,Fproposals reported to be announced on
OL,18,FTuesday.
