OL,3,CFarage pledges 'mass deportation' of
OL,4,Csmall boat arrivals in Reform plans
OL,6,FThey also include deals with third
OL,7,Fcountries, which could include
OL,8,Freviving the Conservatives' Rwanda
OL,9,Flink-up, and sending asylum seekers to
OL,10,FBritish overseas territories such as
OL,11,FAscension Island as a "fallback"
OL,12,Foption.
OL,14,FMr Farage said the plans could see
OL,15,Fhundreds of thousands of people
OL,16,Fdeported and five charter flights
OL,17,Ftaking off from the UK every day.
