OL,3,CFarage pledges 'mass deportation' of
OL,4,Csmall boat arrivals in Reform plans
OL,6,FIt comes amid rising tensions over
OL,7,Fasylum hotels and as the Government
OL,8,Fsaid it planned to appeal against a
OL,9,Fcourt ruling blocking the use of a
OL,10,Fhotel in Epping, Essex.
OL,12,FThe first step of Reform UK's plans
OL,13,Fwould be to leave the European
OL,14,FConvention on Human Rights and to
OL,15,Fscrap the Human Rights Act, followed
OL,16,Fby legislation to bar those who come
OL,17,Fto the UK on small boats from claiming
OL,18,Fasylum.
