OL,3,CFarage pledges 'mass deportation' of
OL,4,Csmall boat arrivals in Reform plans
OL,6,F"The aim of this legislation is mass
OL,7,Fdeportations," Clacton MP Mr Farage
OL,8,Ftold The Times.
OL,10,F"We have a massive crisis in Britain.
OL,11,FIt is not only posing a national
OL,12,Fsecurity threat but it's leading to
OL,13,Fpublic anger that frankly is not very
OL,14,Ffar away from disorder.
OL,16,F"There is only one way to stop people
OL,17,Fcoming into Britain and that is to
OL,18,Fdetain them and deport them."
