OL,4,Csmall boat arrivals in Reform plans
OL,6,FAfter a temporary injunction was
OL,7,Fgranted on Tuesday to Epping Forest
OL,8,FDistrict Council to remove asylum
OL,9,Fseekers from the Bell Hotel in Epping,
OL,10,Fcouncils across the country controlled
OL,11,Fby Labour, the Conservatives and
OL,12,FReform UK are considering following
OL,13,Fsuit with their own legal challenges.
OL,15,FOn Friday, the Home Office said it
OL,16,Fwould appeal against the High Court's
OL,17,Frefusal to allow it to intervene in
OL,18,Fthe case of the Bell Hotel, and to
OL,19,Ffurther appeal against the temporary
OL,20,Finjunction.
