OL,6,FSomani Hotels, the owner of the Bell
OL,7,FHotel, also plans to appeal against
OL,8,Fthe court order blocking the use of
OL,9,Fits site as accommodation for asylum
OL,10,Fseekers.
OL,12,FA wave of protests outside hotels used
OL,13,Fto temporarily house asylum seekers is
OL,14,Fexpected in the coming days.
OL,16,FThe Home Office has a legal obligation
OL,17,Fto provide accommodation to asylum
OL,18,Fseekers who would otherwise be
OL,19,Fdestitute and can move people to
OL,20,Falternatives such as hotels and large
OL,21,Fsites, like former military bases.
