OL,6,FHome Secretary Yvette Cooper said
OL,7,Fministers are working to close hotels
OL,8,Fhousing asylum seekers "as swiftly as
OL,9,Fpossible" as part of an "orderly"
OL,10,Fprogramme that avoids creating
OL,11,Fproblems for other areas.
OL,13,FSouth Norfolk Council said on Friday
OL,14,Fthat it had been informed that the
OL,15,FHome Office intends to stop housing
OL,16,Fasylum seekers at the Park Hotel in
OL,17,Fthe town of Diss.
